\sin^2 x+ \cos x +1 = 0.
1 - \cos^2(x) + \cos(x) + 1 = 0,
\cos^2(x) - \cos(x) - 2 = 0,
\cos x=2
\cos x=-1
x=\pi+n2\pi
n\in \mathbb{Z}.
\tan \frac{x}{2}=t.
\sin x=\frac{2t}{1+t^2}
\cos x=\frac{1-t^2}{1+t^2}.
\left (\frac{2t}{1+t^2}\right )^2+\frac{1-t^2}{1+t^2}+1=0.
4t^2+(1-t^2)(1+t^2)+(1+t^2)^2=0.
4t^2+(1-t^2)(1+t^2)+(1+t^2)^2=4t^2+1-t^4+1+2t^2+t^4=6t^2+2>0.
t = \tan\cfrac{x}{2} = \cfrac{\sin \cfrac{x}2}{\cos \cfrac{x}2}
\cos \cfrac{x}2 = 0
x = \pi + 2\pi n
t
